# Echo — environment variables
#
# Echo needs NO environment variables to run locally or in production:
#   - Brand-voice import is 100% client-side. You upload a posts file you exported
#     from a platform (Instagram / X / LinkedIn) and it's parsed in your browser —
#     no OAuth, no API keys, no secrets. See docs/social-import-upload.md.
#   - The content-kit generator (api/generate.js) reads no secrets either.
#
# If you later add a server-side AI provider, put its key here (SERVER-ONLY) and
# read it via process.env in the api/* function. NEVER prefix a real secret with
# VITE_ — that ships it to the browser. Never paste secrets into chat or commits.
